//   that the vector<1x224x3xf32> transfer_read/write get flattened into
//   vector<672xf32> rank-1 transfers when the underlying memref sub-view
//   is contiguous for those dims. A rank-1 672-element transfer lowers
//   via RVV backend as a vsetvli strip-mined loop at LMUL=m4 VL=128.

